    "This allows analysts to prefer \"recall\" to \"precision\" in the arrival time reading process, possibly resulting in a better catalog with a smaller number of missed events.",
    "Therefore, the performance of the phase association process is important in the earthquake cataloging process.",
    "A popular association method that works well is calculating the theoretical arrival times for a given hypocenter and searching for the hypocenter with many compatible arrival time candidates using a grid search (Draelos et al. 2015).",
    "Recently, the REAL package (Zhang et al. 2019) efficiently processed this task and has, thus, been frequently used.",
    "ML-based methods have also been developed to address this issue."
  ],
